  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db1\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Corona for the US President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is seen in an announcement issued by the White House that United States President Joe Biden has been infected with the Covid-19 virus.",
        "The announcement issued by the White House further states that although 79-year-old Biden is infected with the Covid-19 virus, he is not showing severe symptoms.",
        "The White House has further said that President Biden has received the two doses of the main anti-Covid vaccine and the booster vaccine doses.",
        "White House spokeswoman Karin Jean-Pierre has explained that the President is in quarantine at the White House and his duties are being carried out as usual.",
        "It has been further stated in the announcement issued by the White House that President Joe Biden is taking Paxlovide, an antiviral drug for Covid disease."
      ],
